{"tid":2274398,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"授權票預印姓名 私下出會訊洗白","createTime":"2020-11-06T11:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T11:53:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a88493ad0a25b7d00361a9d49cf1c9f4e51d6b","tid":2274398,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/ANP7OBQSBBF4XBODP5FXCUJKMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FANP7OBQSBBF4XBODP5FXCUJKMQ%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9h5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=eb04f4bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FANP7OBQSBBF4XBODP5FXCUJKMQ%2F&h=ec9efcd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/ANP7OBQSBBF4XBODP5FXCUJKMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n授權票預印姓名 私下出會訊洗白<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9VW8i4htwPOZESTeOjDU5TtkNeQ=/768x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7WEMD3YAENBMTJN25PO3LF5FZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9VW8i4htwPOZESTeOjDU5TtkNeQ%3D%2F768x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7WEMD3YAENBMTJN25PO3LF5FZA.jpg&h=20805d25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■職工會登記局指有足夠證據顯示選舉違反會章及職工會條例。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本報今年9月報道，西醫工會幹事會去年選舉涉及不公，包括授權票預印了會長楊超發的名字，有落選醫生因此向工會投訴，惟楊超發被指多番干預調查，甚至以委任他職及送禮等方法，企圖收買對方。本報自9月16日向西醫工會查詢，但一直未獲回覆。會長楊超發卻在距離新一屆選舉不足一個月，以電郵向會員發出特別會長通訊試圖解畫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被指送禮當掩口費<br />\n<br />\n楊超發在特別會長通訊指稱本報報道不實，但承認授權票預先印上自己名稱，解釋是「印刷上的疏忽」，卻隻字未提選舉是否涉不公，以及授權票的有效性；他稱在幹事會服務逾10年的幹事，均獲頒服務感謝狀，否認「收買」投訴人。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有服務逾10年的幹事表示過去從未收過感謝狀，「有人做咗廿幾年都未收過」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該會過去亦從未發出特別會長通訊，涉事電郵未曾在幹事會上討論。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n負責監管工會運作的職工會登記局，已就上屆選舉事宜介入調查，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TaBRTWtaFdX1MUFN2Q__rvi5zg8=/1568x2437/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N76DFU4FFRHRXHXHO3UQCBBCHU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTaBRTWtaFdX1MUFN2Q__rvi5zg8%3D%2F1568x2437%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN76DFU4FFRHRXHXHO3UQCBBCHU.jpg&h=b13c9d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■義務秘書質疑投票有問題，稱無法肯定其結果真確性。"}]}